{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/linux/reverse-proxy","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I was looking for a reverse proxy for my self-hosted services. The choice is hard. I found 4 options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><del>Apache</del></li>\n<li>nginx</li>\n<li>traefik</li>\n<li>Caddy</li>\n<li>feron (<a href=\"https://www.ferronweb.org/docs/modules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.ferronweb.org/docs/modules/</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ferronweb/ferron\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/ferronweb/ferron</a> )</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"traefik\" style=\"position:relative;\">Traefik<a href=\"#traefik\" aria-label=\"traefik permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>I don't know why I didn't choose <strong>nginx</strong>. I was not a fan of <a href=\"https://www.jenkins.io/doc/book/system-administration/reverse-proxy-configuration-apache/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Apache</a> so I concluded that configuring <strong>nginx</strong> will be the same mess. Or <strong>nginx</strong> has this only in a paid version? Anyway, I decided that small unknown teams could make it better and based on the amount of docs I chose Traefik.</p>\n<p>So on the Edge Router I moved the gui port from 80/443 to 9080/9443 and disabled access from WAN</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">configure\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> gui https-port <span class=\"token number\">9443</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> <span class=\"token function\">service</span> gui listen-address <span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.0.1\ncommit\nsave\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then got a free SSL certificate</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> certbot certonly <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--standalone</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Installed <a href=\"https://doc.traefik.io/traefik/routing/routers/#tls\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Traefik</a> . Configuration based on two files.</p>\n<p>One base config: <strong>traefik.yml</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">global</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">checkNewVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">false</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">sendAnonymousUsage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">false</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">entryPoints</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">web</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">address</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">80</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">http</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">redirections</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">entrypoint</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">to</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> websecure\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">scheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https\n\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">websecure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">address</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">443</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">level</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> DEBUG\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">api</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">insecure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">dashboard</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">providers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">filename</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> dynamic_conf.yml\n\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">docker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">defaultRule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Host(`<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> normalize .Name <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>.docker.localhost`)\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">exposedByDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span> </code></pre></div>\n<p>And the place where you define / add / delete hostnames and services without restarting the server: <strong>dynamic_conf.yml</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">http</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">routers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">social-xyz</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">entrypoints</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> websecure\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">rule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Host(`social.neupokoev.xyz`)\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">service</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> social\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">tls</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">middlewares</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">services</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">social</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">loadBalancer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">servers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://192.168.0.130:8080/\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">tls</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">certificates</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">certFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> /etc/letsencrypt/live/<span class=\"token important\">***/fullchain.pem</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">keyFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> /etc/letsencrypt/live/<span class=\"token important\">***/privkey.pem</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">certFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> /etc/letsencrypt/live/<span class=\"token important\">***/fullchain.pem</span> \n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">keyFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> /etc/letsencrypt/live/<span class=\"token important\">***/privkey.pem</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>And a systemd file <strong>/etc/systemd/system/reverse-proxy.service</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre class=\"language-ini\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"token section\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">Unit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">Description</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">Reverse proxy</span>\n\n<span class=\"token section\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">Service</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">Type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">simple</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">WorkingDirectory</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">/&lt;path_to>/traefik</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">SyslogIdentifier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">traefik</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">ExecStart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">/&lt;path_to>/traefik/traefik --configfile traefik.yml</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">User</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">root</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">Group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">root</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">Restart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">always</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">RestartSec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">20</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">StandardOutput</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">journal</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">StandardError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">journal</span>\n\n<span class=\"token section\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">Install</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">WantedBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">multi-user.target</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"caddy\" style=\"position:relative;\">Caddy<a href=\"#caddy\" aria-label=\"caddy permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>","excerpt":"I was looking for a reverse proxy for my self-hosted services. The choice is hard. I found 4 options: Apache nginx traefik Caddy feron…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#traefik\">Traefik</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#caddy\">Caddy</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/20149e30-9656-5160-ad8f-91d40a228059.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"February 22, 2023","published":"February 04, 2025","lastModified":"February 23, 2023","title":"Reverse Proxy","subtitle":null,"section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/linux/reverse-proxy.md","url":"/linux/reverse-proxy","next":{"excerpt":"","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/linux/read-cpu-frequency.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Read CPU frequency","date":"2023-04-03T00:00:00.000Z","topic":null,"article":null},"id":"5af44ea0-e52d-56a5-8d21-c72dfe1237ae"},"previous":{"excerpt":"A collection of things that I cannot explain Write permissions On one machine with Ubuntu 22.04 all files have write permission for the user…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/linux/linux-mysteries.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Linux mysteries","date":"2022-10-04T00:00:00.000Z","topic":null,"article":null},"id":"564e54b0-b9f0-50bc-be79-4b0a16b7c657"},"recentArticles":[{"excerpt":"The time is now. So you are following the official path","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasa